OL,3,C'It will happen again': Nottingham
OL,4,Cattack families 'fear further
OL,5,Cdisasters'
OL,7,FThe families of the victims of a
OL,8,Fschizophrenic man who fatally stabbed
OL,9,Fthree people in Nottingham said there
OL,10,Fis "real fear" that "further disasters
OL,11,Fare inevitable".
OL,13,FThe comments come after a new report
OL,14,Finto the trust which cared for the
OL,15,Fkiller criticised its mental health
OL,16,Fservices.
