OL,3,C'It will happen again': Nottingham
OL,4,Cattack families 'fear further
OL,5,Cdisasters'
OL,7,FBefore the attacks, the
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust treated Valdo
OL,10,FCalocane, who fatally stabbed Barnaby
OL,11,FWebber, Grace O'Malley Kumar, both 19,
OL,12,Fand Ian Coates, 65, on June 2023.
OL,14,FA report from the Care Quality
OL,15,FCommission (CQC) has criticised its
OL,16,Fmental health services between 2024
OL,17,Fand 2025.
OL,19,FBarnaby's mum Emma told ITV News
OL,20,FCentral that the report filled her
OL,21,Fwith "deep sadness and concern".
