OL,7,FShe said: "There hasn't been
OL,8,Fimprovements in the areas of real
OL,9,Fconcern, and (that) could put the
OL,10,Fpeople of the Nottinghamshire area in
OL,11,Fjeopardy.
OL,13,F"I do fear this is a much broader
OL,14,Fpicture than just being able to say
OL,15,Fthis is an isolated incident (that)
OL,16,Fthis is something that happened that's
OL,17,Fbeing addressed and it won't happen
OL,18,Fagain, because I don't think any of
OL,19,Fthat's true.
