OL,5,Cdisasters'
OL,7,F"It will happen again, it has happened
OL,8,Fagain since, and it will continue to
OL,9,Funtil there are proper fundamental
OL,10,Fchanges to the law and to the
OL,11,Fleadership."
OL,13,FIan Coates' son, James, told ITV News
OL,14,FCentral: "It's a big fear for me, and
OL,15,Fpeople in the city as well because who
OL,16,Fdo you turn to? You can't trust who
OL,17,Fyou should be able to trust.
OL,19,F"These are people you should turn to
OL,20,Fwhen you're in need, and they're just
OL,21,Fnot there to help you."
