OL,7,FThe new report from the CQC said the
OL,8,FTrust's mental health services, which
OL,9,Fcared for Calocane between May 2020
OL,10,Fand September 2022, "were not always
OL,11,Fhumane, dignified or gave high quality
OL,12,Fcare" when treating patients.
OL,14,FBetween May 2024 and August 2025, the
OL,15,FCQC carried out 39 inspections at the
OL,16,Ftrust, before a trust-wide review of
OL,17,Fits leadership was carried out last
OL,18,FSeptember.
