OL,7,FThe report said the trust was found to
OL,8,Fhave breached regulations about how it
OL,9,Fwas managed and asked it to provide an
OL,10,Faction plan.
OL,12,FThe CQC said: "Due to the level and
OL,13,Fnature of risks identified, we have
OL,14,Ftaken enforcement action and asked the
OL,15,Ftrust to make significant improvements
OL,16,Fand to work collaboratively with key
OL,17,Fstakeholders in the wider healthcare
OL,18,Fsystem to support significant
OL,19,Fimprovement."
