OL,3,C'It will happen again': Nottingham
OL,4,Cattack families 'fear further
OL,5,Cdisasters'
OL,7,F"This is an important and crucial
OL,8,Freport when considered in the context
OL,9,Fof the failures in the mental health
OL,10,Fcare services associated with the
OL,11,Fattacks committed by Valdo Calocane
OL,12,Fgiven that he was under the care of
OL,13,Fthe Trust at the time of the attack on
OL,14,F13 June 2023.
OL,16,F"The survivors, Wayne Birkett and
OL,17,FSharon Miller, were only made aware of
OL,18,Fthe existence of this report when
OL,19,Fapproached by the press for comment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
