OL,3,C'It will happen again': Nottingham
OL,4,Cattack families 'fear further
OL,5,Cdisasters'
OL,7,F"They were not consulted by the CQC or
OL,8,Fgiven advance notice of the report
OL,9,Fwhich directly refers to the attack.
OL,10,FThis lack of communication with the
OL,11,Fsurviving victims is not new and
OL,12,Fcannot be allowed to continue.
OL,14,F"We will be writing to the CQC for an
OL,15,Furgent meeting to understand why they
OL,16,Fwere excluded from the process."
OL,18,FA public inquiry into the attacks is
OL,19,Fdue to start in February - and a final
OL,20,Freport of the findings is expected to
OL,21,Fbe published in May 2027.
